ERROR_UNEXPECTED - Static variable in interface cf.Protocol
If the server gets a command that is not expected, for example MAKEMOVE when HELLO is needed first, it sends this message together with the expected keyword, thus in that example: ERROR_UNEXPECTED;;[other expectations]
